"```json\n{\n    \"BRD Questions\": {\n        \"1\": \"What specific metrics or KPIs will be included in the dashboards?\",\n        \"2\": \"Who are the end-users of the dashboards and what are their specific needs?\",\n        \"3\": \"What is the timeline for the development and deployment of the dashboards?\",\n        \"4\": \"What are the specific roles and responsibilities of each stakeholder?\",\n        \"5\": \"What training or support will be provided to users after the dashboards are implemented?\",\n        \"6\": \"How will success be measured after the dashboards are implemented?\",\n        \"7\": \"What specific challenges in cost distribution need to be addressed?\",\n        \"8\": \"What data will be derived from existing reports and how will it be validated?\",\n        \"9\": \"What types of user feedback mechanisms will be in place for the dashboards?\",\n        \"10\": \"What are the specific technological constraints, if any, of the existing SAP framework?\",\n        \"11\": \"Are there any compliance or regulatory considerations that need to be taken into account?\",\n        \"12\": \"How will the integration with Qlik Sense be tested and validated?\",\n        \"13\": \"What specific data extraction methods will be used to ensure real-time data updates?\",\n        \"14\": \"What will be the process for maintaining and updating the dashboards post-deployment?\",\n        \"15\": \"Who will be responsible for ongoing maintenance and support of the dashboards?\",\n        \"16\": \"Are there any anticipated risks or issues that could impact the project timeline?\",\n        \"17\": \"What specific resources are required for the project and how will they be allocated?\",\n        \"18\": \"What will be the process for handling any discrepancies in data interpretation?\",\n        \"19\": \"What measures will be taken to ensure the dashboards remain scalable?\",\n        \"20\": \"Is there a backup plan in place if the integration with SAP or Qlik Sense fails?\"\n    }\n}\n```"